msgid "This effect/filter takes the red, green and blue channels in the video and separates them by a given x and y amount to produce a rainbowish effect similar to the Tik Tok logo. Compare the :doc:`/effects_and_filters/video_effects/stylize/rgba_shift` effect which essentially does the same but allows individual shifting of the RGB and Alpha channels and has the ability to determine the edge operation. Also compare the :doc:`/effects_and_filters/video_effects/stylize/chroma_shift` effect."
